-61001 means that NIE couldn't initialize the network card.  Check the
default internet setup in your (default) worksite.  If it's not set to the
internet setup you're currently using, then when your Newton reboots, NPDS
watcher will try to use the default internet setup to reconnect, and if
this is invalid (ie. it's set to use a card that isn't inserted or doesn't
exist) then it will emit this error.

